  "name": "The Chief Clerk",
  "description": "Gregor's office supervisor who arrives at the apartment when Gregor fails to catch his morning train. His visit escalates the crisis: he threatens Gregor's job through the locked door, and when Gregor finally emerges in his insect form, the clerk flees without a word. He is the outside world's sole witness to the transformation, and his departure seals the family's isolation.",
